After some of the Sherlock episodes your mind acts weirdly.Every time use see it you see some suspense.The actors like Benedict Cumberbatch , Martin Freeman have performed well.Many episodes end in suspense. This is a humorous,adventurous,thrilling TV series and is especially for adult and teenagers. The actors and their description in the book is suitable.This Sherlock is a bit different he uses a mobile and a laptop .The story in the TV Series is very much modified from the book.This is a Sherlock in the modern world.After you see this TV series, you would never believe ,Sherlock Homes is a imaginary character. And at last "I BELIEVE IN 221B Baker Street".